    • disableTest

      public CreateRequest disableTest()
      Whether to test the request prior to creating it. By default this is set to true. Disabling tests means that gas fees will be lost if a transaction fails on the blockchain. Disable with caution.
      Returns:
      this request.

    • testOnly

      public CreateRequest testOnly()
      When true a transaction will be tested, but won't be saved or sent. This is handy if you wish test settings without submitting any blockchain transactions.
      Returns:
      this request.
